---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"spec\"])"
---
Inspect annotations and tooling dependencies for a spec

Usage: loom spec [OPTIONS] <LABEL>

Arguments:
  <LABEL>  Spec label to inspect

Options:
      --deps              Print the unique nixpkgs names referenced by spec annotation targets
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi, direct]
  -h, --help              Print help
